#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1220
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "这片虚空一无所有，连半颗星辰都看不见。你凝望着这片虚无轻叹一声，静待着G的承诺将如何兑现。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1221
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "无边无际的黑暗向四面八方延伸，视野所及尽是虚空。这里万籁俱寂，连通讯频道里都听不到半点背景杂音。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1222
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "有那么一瞬间，你感觉好像被注视着。当然，你一回头，还是什么都没看到，不过以防万一你也留了个心眼。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1223
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//textList[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY_TEXT\"]/text[4]"
msgstr "飞船四周彻底的空无一物让你神经紧绷。你本以为至少会看到星辰、星云，甚至能窃听到反抗军的通讯……但这里连需要戒备的舰队都不存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1228
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_TARTARUS_EMPTY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1245
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘强大的金色战舰裂成碎片，自身的巨大重量使其向内坍缩。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1247
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1252
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "幻灵通常不擅长船员间的格斗，毕竟他们的专长是破坏。但不知怎的，凭着自身的贪婪，奥古斯都竟克服了这一弱点，让你打了一场着实艰难的战斗。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1254
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1266
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你们抵达了标注为\"额外悬赏\"的坐标。正如所料，一艘设计独特的飞船正环绕信标运行，一感应到你的存在便发来了通讯。这艘船的船体通体似乎由纯金铸成；传闻这样一艘船只属于有史以来最富有的那位幽灵——奥古斯都。他死于叛变，堪称鬼魂中的鬼财主。\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\"听好了，吾劝尔等速速撤离，以免汝那锈迹斑斑的破船玷污了本座金舰的无上光辉！若敢违抗，休怪吾用纯金炮弹将尔等舰船拆成碎片——待本座回收残骸，财富必将更胜往昔！\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1273
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1275
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "意识到此战不可避免，你果断启动武器系统，向敌舰发起进攻。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1277
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1285
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你们在残骸中还意外发现了一件特殊武器！其设计完全超乎你的认知，你推测这必定是那些神秘生物特制的型号。\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t更令人惊讶的是，一个与你刚消灭的对手容貌相同的家伙竟出现在船上，身形逐渐凝聚成形。在你开火前，他立刻宣誓效忠，盛赞你将他从G的控制中解放出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1289
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_AUGUSTUS_DEFEAT\"]/crewMember"
msgstr "奥古斯都"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1304
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "那艘蜘蛛般的舰船很快便崩溃并停止了响应。你暗自庆幸自己没有蜘蛛恐惧症，否则这场战斗会艰难得多……"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1306
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/destroyed/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1311
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "蜘蛛是难缠的对手，它们相对较小的体型下隐藏着凶猛的战斗潜力。尽管萨利似乎更偏向于支援单位，但她也不是那么容易杀死的。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1313
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//ship[@name=\"FR_SHIP_CHAOS_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/deadCrew/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1325
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你抵达了标注为\"额外悬赏\"的坐标。正如所料，一艘设计独特的飞船正环绕信标运行，一感应到你的存在便发来了通讯。这艘船的船体似乎主要由血肉构成，正应和了那些古老传说——一位科学家为了保命，竟将自己与宠物蜘蛛融为一体。\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\"哦，我的天呐！这不是新朋友嘛！亲爱的，请别不高兴，可一股超越我控制的力量命令我必须与你一战！这对你来说确实很不幸，但至少我向你保证……到了死后世界，我会陪伴你的，毕竟你可是我的新朋友呀！\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1331
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "准备战斗！"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1333
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "意识到此战不可避免，你果断启动武器系统，向敌舰发起进攻。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1335
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1343
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY_DEFEAT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你们在残骸中还意外发现了一件特殊武器！你以前从未见过任何与之哪怕略微相似的东西，因此推测这必定是那些神秘生物定制的型号。\n"
"\t\t\n"
"此外，一个与你刚杀死的那人容貌相同的家伙出现在你的船上，身形渐渐从虚空中显现。就在你准备开火之际，他立刻宣誓效忠，盛赞你将他从 G 的控制下解放了出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml:1347
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_sector_tartarus.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_REVENANT_SALLY_DEFEAT\"]/crewMember"
msgstr "萨利"
